## Naming Conventions

<!-- Add project-specific naming patterns. -->
<!-- The framework defaults (PascalCase entities, camelCase hooks, etc.) still apply. -->

| Layer | Pattern | Example |
|-------|---------|---------|
| Entity | PascalCase noun | `Order.ts` |
| Value Object | PascalCase descriptive | `OrderStatus.ts` |
| Port (interface) | PascalCase with suffix | `OrderRepository.ts` |
| Use Case | PascalCase verb phrase | `GetOrders.ts` |
| DTO | PascalCase + Dto | `OrderSummaryDto.ts` |
| Infrastructure | PascalCase + adapter prefix | `StripePaymentRepository.ts` |
| Hook | camelCase + use prefix | `useOrders.ts` |
| UI Component | PascalCase | `OrderCard.tsx` |
| Test | same name + `.test.ts` | `GetOrders.test.ts` |
| Spec | kebab-case + `.feature` | `order-checkout.feature` |

